## Diagram Relasi File

### Backend — Alur Request

```mermaid
graph LR
    Client["Frontend / Browser"] -->|"HTTP Request"| SRV["server.js"]
    SRV -->|"app.use('/api/projects')"| RT["projectRoutes.js"]
    SRV -->|"app.post('/api/seed')"| SC["seedController.js"]
    RT -->|"GET /"| PC["projectController.js<br/>(getProjects)"]
    RT -->|"POST /"| PC2["projectController.js<br/>(createProject)"]
    RT -->|"PUT /:id"| PC3["projectController.js<br/>(updateProject)"]
    RT -->|"DELETE /:id"| PC4["projectController.js<br/>(deleteProject)"]
    PC --> DB["db.js → MySQL Pool"]
    PC2 --> DB
    PC3 --> DB
    PC4 --> DB
    SC --> DB
    SRV -->|"initDatabase()"| DB
```

| File | Fungsi | Dipakai Oleh |
|---|---|---|
| [server.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/server.js) | Entry point, middleware CORS, auto-migration DB, dummy data awal | — (root) |
| [db.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/config/db.js) | Membuat connection pool ke MySQL (Railway/lokal) | [server.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/server.js), [projectController.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/controllers/projectController.js), [seedController.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/controllers/seedController.js) |
| [projectController.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/controllers/projectController.js) | Query DB, hitung status EVM, format respons JSON | [projectRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/routes/projectRoutes.js) |
| [seedController.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/controllers/seedController.js) | Generate 50 proyek random + relasi lengkap | [server.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/server.js) (route langsung) |
| [projectRoutes.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/routes/projectRoutes.js) | Definisi endpoint CRUD `/api/projects` | [server.js](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/server.js) |
| [init_db.sql](file:///c:/Users/Asus/Downloads/Dashboard%20EMP/backend/init_db.sql) | ❌ Skema SQL lama, tidak di-import file manapun | — |

