## Dependency Flow (Data)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Netlify as Netlify (React)
    participant Railway as Railway (Express)
    participant MySQL

    Browser->>Netlify: GET /posture atau /list atau /progress
    Netlify->>Browser: Mengirim React SPA (HTML+JS)
    Browser->>Railway: fetch(VITE_API_URL + "/api/projects")
    Railway->>MySQL: SELECT projects + metrics + issues + timeline + members
    MySQL-->>Railway: Raw rows
    Railway-->>Browser: JSON { projects[], stats{}, topIssues[] }
    Note over Browser: React memproses & render charts, tabel, KPI
```
